<db:para>This is a collection of small QML examples relating to right to left(RTL) localization support.</db:para>
<db:para>Layout direction shows RTL layouting. Layout mirroring shows automatic mirroring of horizontal layouts in RTL locales. Text Alignment shows automatic mirroring of text alignment in RTL locales.</db:para>
